column1: Adventurousness
I seek more adventure than before.
I seek to visit new places more than before.
I seek more changes than before.
Compassion
Compared to before, now I feel others’ emotions more.
I inquire about others’ well-being more than before.
I do things for others more than before.
Conscientiousness
Compared to before, now I believe more that laws should be strictly enforced.
I try to follow the rules more than before.
I like order more than before.
Emotional Stability
I am more relaxed than before.
I am less easily frustrated than before.
I feel less frequently blue than before.
Introversion
I seek quiet more than before.
I enjoy silence more than before.
I enjoy my privacy more than before.
Spirituality
Compared to before, now I practice religion more.
I am a more spiritual person than before.
I  keep my faith even during hard times more than before.
